snippet.title: Live w/ Amber and Jaime: Answering Questions from Young Potential Real Estate Investors - CYL Pod
snippet.description:
In this episode of Construct Your Life Podcast with Austin Linney, we have two new investors Amber and Jamie who are formulating their strategy to get their first properties. We also have Matt Teifke of Teifke Real Estate who together with Austin answers real estate questions from Amber Adams and Jaime Aguilar.

They talk about the state of the current real estate market and why you should focus majorly on buying properties rather than selling. They also share their golden tips on how to approach offering value to your mentors when you’re just starting in the real estate industry.

Listen in to learn the right process of getting the right real estate deals.

“Define who you are, show up every day as that person, and the right clients will find you.”- Austin [50:29]

What You Will Discover:
[3:13] How to go about starting your real estate journey as a young person.

[7:12] Find people who align with your goals as a serious real estate investor.

[19:58] Tips on how to offer value to potential mentors when you’re new in the real estate game.

[36:14] Where and how to start the process of getting property deals.

[42:42] The state of the real estate market right now and how to buy the right properties.

[46:57] Lessons from experienced investors on how to separate money from success. 

Relevant Links:
Website: https://www.trehomes.com/
LinkedIn: https://www.linkedin.com/in/matt-teifke-90672438/

#podcast
